  <steps>
    <step num="0">Cut the mango in half lengthwise, around the pit. </step>
    <step num="1">Press the mango halves down along the edge of glass to separate the flesh from the skin. </step>
    <step num="2">Add the mango to a blender, along with the sugar, milk, and yogurt. Blend until smooth. </step>
    <step num="3">Pour the mango lassi into a glass. </step>
    <step num="4">Enjoy! </step>
  </steps>
